column5: Anyone hit up Rice Lake this past weekend? How's the ice? How's the bite?
Can't help you Stoty...haven't been on or near Rice. Just thought I'd bump. Somebody help the man out.  P.S.  How's the pooch doin?
Haha, thanks dude! Appreciated!  The pooch is fine thanks! BUSY though! So busy, I have only been out on the ice once! lol Hoping to get out this week at least once though.  Cheers!
